**AI Product Card Generator**

An AI-powered web application that generates product card details such as title, description, and tags based on a product name and category. The app uses Google Gemini AI through a REST API and displays the generated content in a clean, responsive product card UI.

 /*Assignment Details*/

Assignment 2: AI Content Generator for Product Cards

Problem Statement

Create a web app that generates product card details (title, description, tags) using AI and displays them visually.

/*Features*/

 Input form for Product Name and Category

 AI-generated:

        Product Title

        Short Description

        Relevant Tags

 Visually styled product card

 Loading indicator during AI response

 Fully responsive design

 Error handling for invalid inputs and API failures

 /*Tech Stack*/

Frontend: React (Vite)

Styling: CSS (Responsive & animated UI)

AI Model: Google Gemini 2.5 Flash (Free Tier)

API Integration: REST API (fetch)

State Management: React useState

 /*AI Model Used*/

Model: gemini-2.5-flash

Why this model?

Free to use (with API key)

Fast response

Ideal for short text generation

Suitable for frontend AI projects